---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Nearcon 2024 — AES" bodyClass="inner-page">

  <div class="container-fluid event-hero">
    <div class="event-hero-inner">
      <div class="event-hero-left">
        <div class="event-location">Bangkok, Thailand</div>
        <div class="event-title">Nearcon<br />2024</div>
        <div class="event-tagline">
          Near hosted their annual flagship event for 1,500 attendees in Bangkok, leaning into a Thai-market theme at the main conference with 3 featured side events.
        </div>
        <div class="event-hero-photo">
          <div class="event-hero-photo-item" style="background-image: url('/images/work1.png')"></div>
          <div class="event-hero-photo-item" style="background-image: url('/images/work2.png')"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="event-hero-right">
        <div class="event-detail-card">
          <div class="event-detail-block">
            <div class="event-detail-heading">Location</div>
            <p>Nearcon 2024 was brought to Bangkok alongside Devcon. As our first time working in the area, we location and vendor scouted for a full week in May 2024 in preparation for the November event. We made great connections, found the perfect venues, and learned the city and culture — coming back to the client with plenty of intel for further planning.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="event-detail-block">
            <div class="event-detail-heading">Production</div>
            <p>Near's creative team is always fun to work with — they love taking ideas to the max and thinking outside the box, while staying true to Near's core values. We leaned into Bangkok themes while honoring nature and local culture, a perfect marriage for the client.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="event-detail-block">
            <div class="event-detail-heading">Side Events</div>
            <p>Three side events, three distinctly different locations — a botanical greenhouse, an antique furniture shop/cafe, and a boutique nightclub. Different vibes, different purposes, all meeting the unique needs of the client.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid event-gallery">
    <div class="event-gallery-inner">
      <div class="gallery-grid">
        <div class="gallery-placeholder gallery-large" style="background-image: url('/images/work3.png')"></div>
        <div class="gallery-placeholder" style="background-image: url('/images/work5.png')"></div>
        <div class="gallery-placeholder" style="background-image: url('/images/work7.png')"></div>
        <div class="gallery-placeholder gallery-large" style="background-image: url('/images/work9.png')"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid event-back">
    <div class="event-back-inner">
      <a href="/work" class="cr-btn white ex-padding">← Back to All Events</a>
    </div>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>
